    <string name="api_timeout_usb_tip">On a physical phone: open the same /api/v1/health URL in Chrome here — if it hangs, the phone cannot reach your PC (wrong IP, different Wi‑Fi, or firewall).\n\nUSB cable to this PC: on the PC run adb reverse tcp:3000 tcp:3000 — then set the base URL to http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/v1/ and tap Test connection.\n\nOn Windows, allow inbound TCP port 3000 (Node.js) in Windows Defender Firewall for Private networks.</string>
